window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A Legendary Lost Weapon Has Returned</b></p> <p>As Princess Victoria prepares to reclaim her throne, Trent Marston learns the location of an enchanted magebow lost centuries ago. Emerald, Ruby and Sapphire’s foster sister, has re-emerged in the hands of the enemy. If Trent can find her, he’ll have another powerful ally on his side.</p> <p>After Trent heads to the remote nation of Clarion to save Emerald, he is drawn into a civil war that threatens to tear the small but fierce nation apart. Rumors claim the Clarion insurgents are led by a fierce hex mage with brilliant red hair, suggesting Revca’s long-lost sister is still alive.</p> <p>Powerful forces rise against him. But with his loyal tribe at his side, Trent can face any challenge.</p>"; 
